    EasyEDA Pro has been released for several years and can completely replace the EasyEDA Std.
    1. The features are more comprehensive and powerful. Features comparison
    2. Better performance and no pressure on large designs.
    3. The feature is constantly updated, making drawing more efficient.
    4. Support the batch migration of EasyEDA Std libraries and projects. Projects migration tutorials.
    5. Support on premise hosting for enterprise. Apply trial for free

    It is recommended to gradually transfer to the EasyEDA Pro for project creation starting from now.
    The EasyEDA Std will no longer add new features, and enter maintenance phase.

                            Recommended migrate the Std edition projects to the Pro edition, the Pro edition is more features powerful, and more more smoother. How to migrate:
                            1. Download and login the Pro edition. https://easyeda.com/page/download
                            2. Via: Top Menu - File - Migrate Standard...
                            3. Select the projects or libraries to migrate.
                            4. If your projects are saved at local, you can compress the schematic and PCB as a zip file, and then import it to the Pro edition. Via: Top Menu - File - Import - EasyEDA(Standard).
